The antioxidant activities including ABTS and DPPH scavenging activities as well as ferric reducing antioxidant power (FRAP) of the isolated compounds were determined as we previously reported (
Karnjanapratum and Benjakul, 2015
; 
Benjakul et al., 2014
). The results were expressed as mmol Trolox equivalent (TE)/g sample.
